Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:54.44,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰かのためなら悪くはないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:01:00.28,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}理由らしいものは今日も　…見えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:05.80,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧なリアル　点と点をつなぐ光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:12.54,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}消えそうな夢を　そっと握りしめてみる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:22.17,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}僕たちの声が  君の癒やせない傷痕に届けば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.77,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ナガレテク　雲の速さへと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:33.79,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}置いてかれないように叫ぶ　今日のエチュード
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:41.13,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}カナエタイ　静かな絶望の先に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.04,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}新しい　はじまりへのページ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:48.78,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その手をとって　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.59,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}君が望むから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.05,OPjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}どこまでも行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:54.44,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}若是為了誰  這無可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:01:00.28,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}今天依然沒看見像樣的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.41,0:01:05.80,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}曖昧交織的現實  點點相連的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:12.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}嘗試著握住那轉眼即逝的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.73,0:01:22.17,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我們的聲音  若能傳達到你那無法治癒的傷痕的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}宛如流雲的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:33.79,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}為了不再置之不理  放聲唱出今天的練習曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:41.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}渴望著那寂靜的絕望的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.04,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}是通向全新伊始的篇章
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:48.78,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}牽住你的手  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.59,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}正如你所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:57.05,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}一路向前

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.47,0:00:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長  生意興隆真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為之前那騷動  客人們都蠻擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  他來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥

Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:10.92,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fsp-1}翻譯:絆咲    Miya　校對:千葉命 特效:我們的夏天　後期:毛球／阿爽

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊  哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別輸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  輸掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲哥毫無戰術可言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  邊想邊玩誰做得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿俊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這段時間都去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  為什麼都不和我們聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.16,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子身體不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩遊戲真厲害  雖然我在後面觀戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但出招太快  根本看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看來就像靜止不動一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.83,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分毫移動都逃不過我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像靜止不動一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是彩夏的男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我們只是同為園藝部部員而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很煩人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又蠢又煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想把我帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那一定是因為擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她才不會擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.53,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己都不去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是想讓自己安心而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去扮演一個照顧沒用的哥哥的溫柔妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是當心點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像我的替代品一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel·Fix
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.68,0:05:00.18,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(500,0)}關於你

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學  你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和你在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海嗎  想讓你幫忙買點東西過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？聽不太清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就繼續玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PWRB很好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  阿俊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  他吃了像藥丸一樣的東西後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變得怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又嗑藥啊  他還是老樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.17,0:05:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗑藥？哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對彩夏說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道哥哥在嗑藥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他有說什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才表情明顯動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定有什麼瞞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.22,0:06:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  這正是坦白的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪都無所謂  倒是你聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別對他們說多餘的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事我會聯絡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 墓見坂叫我代他向你問聲好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在墓見坂先生那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓見坂？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  我也只見過兩三次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是研究生專門研究植物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫長的暑假已經過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看見諸位精神抖擻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我深感欣慰  然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海  愛麗絲的午飯做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲  午飯來咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要幹什麼  我又不是晚飯的殘羹冷炙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她護理頭髮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要美容技術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.51,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是學會了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.93,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後就不准你來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡一直都是那麼吵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工作委託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才做了一半啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該有什麼能幫忙的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事已經出人命了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨這次我不希望有一般人牽涉進來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把結義兄弟當做一般人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在這一帶流傳著新型毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓你調查販賣途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒品的名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Angel·Fix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你知道點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在不說也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把下面的三個人叫上來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定嗎？阿俊真的有那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他說了Angel·Fix
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笨蛋  居然對這麼危險的東西出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fix是外行人在販賣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買家一般是將其掰散的或者是弄成粉狀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再轉手賣出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才沒有販賣途徑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的頭是誰也毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  唯一能確認的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿俊擁有大量這種毒品的原因不外乎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接購買或是用來販賣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那看來有必要立刻找到阿俊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他全盤托出了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說這鬧出人命了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我不想讓你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏拜託你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  盯著她別讓她發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛村哥也好過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我一人被排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.44,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玫歐那事我不也幫到忙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.08,0:09:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.11,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夥剛才都說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲學長他們也進事務所了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼的  不是什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:09:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後俊哥有聯絡你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥有關嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把我趕出來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得我礙事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不方便讓我聽的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學也一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他…重要的事情從來不對我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.00,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是一聲不吭地走掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很煩人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.07,0:10:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明那麼要好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻什麼都不願和我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學  你這樣就和哥哥沒區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像是我的替代品一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…替代品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你哥哥的替代品嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.81,0:10:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我應該能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然俊哥不行  但如果是我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.14,0:10:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要說這種話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小心翼翼地站立在那之上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪和水交織起來的素白色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從掛滿透明冰冷水珠的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光潤美麗的松樹枝上  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給心愛的妹妹取來最後的一餐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？無精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被篠崎說什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.74,0:11:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出園藝部不就得了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨天那事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己也不清楚不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我錯了我會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不清楚你也會道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不說我怎麼會懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.68,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是說算了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不懂怎樣才算做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此  現在的我能做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓彩夏重拾歡笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.74,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以靠近哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面剛灑過藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.14,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CGM？（擊退色狼機器）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的  對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從裡面的字母開始讀起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MGC（美園高中園藝部）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼做出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拜託善喜哥做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不上學該不會就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  合適嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有倒是有啦

Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.41,0:14:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35}免費附送給你啦  善喜

Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你是聽哥哥說了些什麼對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會突然說那種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥說什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.01,0:14:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說彩夏不去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不太擅長和別人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常會一個人待在屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在教室怎麼待怎麼不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.57,0:14:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就上了屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就看見藤島同學也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始我只是想和你說說話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是鼓不起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就搬了幾個花盆來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣裝成做社團活動就有藉口上屋頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道哥哥跟你說了些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學絕對不是替代品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為藤島同學是獨一無二的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後的一個多月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋頂積聚的陰暗  被夏天的天空帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.02,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和彩夏像以前一樣有說有笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  當天空被秋天的雲所覆蓋的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.62,0:16:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股陰暗又延伸開來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英語要絕望了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.53,0:16:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.21,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事情拜託兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的文化祭會佔用屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能在這幾天把花盆收拾一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.84,0:16:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像好深奧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我受愛麗絲所托從大學藥學部的資料架裡借來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能製成毒品的植物資料以及成分表
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也完全看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這一疊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近一個月涉谷區內涉及到毒品的報警記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宏哥那邊有收穫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿俊就跟人間蒸發了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說警察總局的大人物秘密地來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好像還什麼都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.68,0:17:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  原來是鳴海小弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊  害我還以為是彩夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏還在維護溫室要晚些再來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們差不多撤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.26,0:17:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在那晃悠到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點上來  跟阿宏一起上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是摩卡熊的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那愛麗絲那邊拜託你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡要好好收拾好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計彩夏差不多要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  哲哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿俊會碰這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不懂那些會碰毒品的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.41,0:18:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.11,0:18:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.24,0:18:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.08,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最近一個月被送往附近醫院病人的名單
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我交給愛麗絲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴海也要來試試味道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋的新作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是提拉米蘇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也要試試主流路線
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也幫忙了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了彩夏  你也快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「拉我一把」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提拉米蘇好像是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學真博學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啦  之前姐姐跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首個製作提拉米蘇的人大概也是這種心情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屋頂打算什麼時候收拾？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  果然還是不能不收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再在那多做些社團活動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.18,0:20:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤島同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.84,0:20:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天找老師商量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是文化祭要用 那麼急是清理不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡是我們的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那只是漂亮話…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我姑且也算是園藝部的成員啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.42,0:21:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩夏的笑臉之前也見過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我現在能清晰地回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.79,0:21:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那無瑕的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我在那時挽留住她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.49,0:21:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者問問她發生了什麼事的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.63,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說不定根本不需要打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神所寫下的記事本其中的一頁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了彩夏  我受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.07,0:23:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不是過去的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.34,0:23:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找失去了的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我要成為偵探助手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.69,0:23:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:11.79,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}路地裏には暗い暗い灯り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:16.27,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}そこに集う羽虫達のよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:20.48,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}もがく僕らは cry cry 共に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.96,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}秘めた思いをくすぶらせてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:29.63,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}「何をすればいい」　それがわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:33.98,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限の意味恐れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:38.29,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}しびれ切らした両の足が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.51,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}立ち上がれとせがんでいる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.98,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}全て運命だなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.12,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}神の落書きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.60,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}丸めて捨てるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:59.66,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}たったひとつの冴えたやり方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.84,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}いつも胸に抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:09.90,EDjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}夜明け　睨みつけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:11.79,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}小巷裡昏暗的燈光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:16.27,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}引得小飛蟲紛紛聚集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:20.48,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我們心急如焚一同哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:24.96,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}煽起深藏心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:29.63,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我不知該何去何從
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:33.98,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}無限的意義使我畏縮不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:38.29,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}面對那失去知覺的雙腳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:44.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}我央求道  快快站起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:50.98,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}一切都是命中注定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:53.12,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只是神輕描淡寫的塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.60,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}看我把它揉成一團一併扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.78,0:22:59.66,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}唯一行之有效的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.90,0:23:03.84,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}就是謹記於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:09.90,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}怒視拂曉吧
